title: DEATHMATCH 007 (2013) (Boom) (Digital) (G85-Empire)
description:
All bets are off as Dragonfly faces the prospect of battling the godlike Anti-Meridian should Meridian himself perish, while outside the arena the Rat struggles to decipher Glyph's secret messages before it's too late. Who will rise above the ever-accumulating body pile as "Deathmatch" hurtles towards the semi-finals?!

Written by Paul Jenkins, with art by Carlos Magno, "Deathmatch" #7 hits shelves Wednesday, July 3rd!
